headline: Pat Roche Elected to The EMCOR Group, Inc. Board of Directors
summary: NORWALK, Conn., October 29, 2025--EMCOR Group, Inc. (the "Company") (NYSE: EME) announced today the election of Pat Roche to the Company’s Board of Directors, effective October 27, 2025.
